Install Instructions:

1 - Your Arduino must be connected to your computer. 
	1.1 - Check in which port it is mapped on your computer.
2 - Export environment variables to where your arduino and avr are located.
3 - Navigate to coursework-1 folder and run compile.sh script.
	3.1 - If it does not work that way, please, make sure that files are located
		properly just like script requires.
4 - Wait untill instalation is done on your arduino.
5 - Play! :)
